amarskenderovic-pset2
Mad Libs app

amarskenderovic-week1 11196041 madlibs app with 4 different Activities. (also possible in landscape-mode)

1- Homepage with an explanation about the app and a button to begin.

2- Second activity to choose from 5 different stories and a button to create the selected story.

3- Third activity to input the corresponding placeholders, with a counter of how many words are left and a button to continue only if the requirements are met.

4- Last activity to show the output of the input from the 3rd activity and a button to try and create a new story.
